E), key_fn=None, max_states: int = 20000, max_depth: int = 80):` — Generic clone BFS over observational keys. Use small max_states first.; calls: arr, deque, goal_fn, int, key_fn, len\n- L189--190 `def level_goal(base_level: int):`\n\n## solve.py\n- L3--13 `def solve(env): # dispatch to the per-level player for the current level, in a loop`; calls: fn, getattr\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
